                "efficiency with a set of gamma-ray standards (152Eu,",
                "137Cs, 60Co, 133Ba, and 241Am, uncertainty of the",
                "activities <1%, Czech Institute for Metrology,",
                "Department of Ioniz. Radia-n) for various geometries."
