          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Thin targets of 231Pa were prepared by",
                "electrodeposition on silver disks (99.99%, Alfa",
                "Aesar) of 0.25-mm thickness and 20- mm diameter used",
                "as cathode. Aliquots of 231Pa in 0.4 M ammonium",
                "oxalate were added to the electrolysis cell",
                "containing 8.9 mL of 4% ammonium chloride/4%",
                "ammonium oxalate solution and 10 mu-L of",
                "concentrated hydrofluoric acid.",
                "Targets were contained 10.4-19.1 mu-g of 231Pa.",
                "Subsequently the silver disks were covered with",
                "aluminum foils (34.9-mu-m thick., 99.99%, Alfa Aesar)",
                "acting as catcher foils to avoid any losses of",
                "activity by recoil processes."
              ]
            }
          ],
