          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Thick targets for production runs were prepared from",
                "protactinium pentoxide. The resulting oxide was",
                "ground in a mortar together with 2 mg of zinc",
                "stearate and aliquots of 235 mg of protactinium",
                "pentoxide, corresponding to 200 mg of 231Pa, were",
                "pressed into circular pellets with a diameter of 6",
                "mm at a pressure of 5 tons/cm2.",
                "The final pellets had a diameter of 4.9 mm and a",
                "thickness of 1.3-1.4 mm. Subsequently, the pellets",
                "were enclosed in silver capsules made from silver",
                "disks (30-mm diameter, 0.25-mm thickness), which were",
                "welded gastight."
              ]
            }
          ],
